data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkRqMQMG86W8&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=f31f184d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kRqMQMG86W8</a><br />\n<br />\n經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「呆帳會一個月造成的，或是一年造成嗎？所以呢做為國家領導人的競逐者，如果連這樣的<span style=\"color: red;\">基本知識都沒有，我們真的為連先生感到擔心</span>」、「<span style=\"color: red;\">你還不感謝偶，你還要邀功</span>」、「過去你做過院長、你做過省主席，<span style=\"color: red;\">為什麼你不做？有的是機會阿</span>。同樣的，北宜高速公路雪山隧道，為什麼你打不通？做了9年打不通，我們打通了你知道不知道？明年就要通車了」、「這種高度的執行力，難道你完全都沒有聽到嗎？縱使你不去了解，也應該會聽到。聽到以後你可以問你很多朋友，我們有吹牛嗎？真的嗎？還是我們隨便講的。<span style=\"color: red;\">我還是覺得要做為一個國家的領導人，很多事情看問題不要只看一半，要看清楚一點，謝謝</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />串到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d212eb851d3dedc7807e1e929c407330387da9d","tid":1824674,"uid":1275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kRqMQMG86W8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkRqMQMG86W8&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=57203514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kRqMQMG86W8</a><br />\n講阿扁經典一定係呢段，小英對韓總機都無咁精彩"},{"pid":"7770c9d91fe8444a7e660cc0958b49ab8bd77d2e","tid":1824674,"uid":12701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7bbb878c47b34ae54afa91b7c3e5961c705a384","tid":1824674,"uid":1275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95a10a2ac940d1bd72683e18c3c577b4b745feb9","tid":1824674,"uid":12701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35e56cca0a4a01ebd5d901363a1a88b50004b681","tid":1824674,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=